<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='679078' id='t-679078'>And after all, it has its own internal aesthetics.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='682567' id='t-682567'>These branching patterns that we see</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='684371' id='t-684371'>we see across all forms, scales of nature,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='686921' id='t-686921'>from river deltas to lightning strikes,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='689721' id='t-689721'>from our own blood vessels to neural networks.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='693757' id='t-693757'>There's clearly significant rules at play</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='696220' id='t-696220'>in this simple yet complex organism,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='698485' id='t-698485'>and no matter what our disciplinary
