<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='702277' id='t-702277'>there's a great deal that we can learn</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='704060' id='t-704060'>from observing and engaging</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='705829' id='t-705829'>with this beautiful, brainless blob.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:59
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='708950' id='t-708950'>I give you Physarum polycephalum.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:03
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='712165' id='t-712165'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:04
</data>
